{"tid":138920,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲教路點樣應付老屎忽","createTime":"2017-03-01T04:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T04:24:27.000Z","uid":2945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96b72ec0849c05567dc9055d34c63e6dbf206ecf","tid":138920,"uid":2945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"有個老屎忽前兩日請咗假，咁啱有樣佢負責嘅嘢急住今日要，於是上司叫我跟住先<br />\n其實當日已經幫佢做得七七八八，咁咪留返埋尾嗰啲等佢自己跟<br />\n<br />\n結果第二日佢返嚟，見啲嘢喺我到，就話：<br />\n「哦～你跟緊呀」<br />\n然後走咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我將啲文件擺返去佢枱面示意畀返佢做<br />\n<br />\n後來上司交咗啲新嘢要佢返落去<br />\n隔咗一段時間，條友話自己有急事要行開吓，叫我幫佢做埋佢<br />\n我：「我都唔得閒喎，要去第二間房做嘢喎」<br />\n佢：「你拎埋過去做吖，我真係趕住出去」<br />\n然後頭也不回咁走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁啱上司行過見啲嘢仲未搞掂，又叫我幫吓手<br />\n結果我都係幫佢做咁啲，再將啲嘢攤喺到期望佢自己處理埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直到今日返嚟佢一直冇掂過啲文件，而佢下晝又要出去，睇怕最後上司都係叫我做埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇方法拒絕？條友成日側側膊將佢啲嘢射畀我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：新入職，打算長做，好多嘢仲要問，未敢得罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3277d601b2631efc1935585a2a15a5cc4320b588","tid":138920,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:07:00.000Z","msg":"無嫁喇 硬食<br />\n鬼叫你係新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff44515ef4cffa724311d974f6b938677f74ceea","tid":138920,"uid":74911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"捐落佢枱底"},{"pid":"e8bfc195d14fe823df33d3ac9bb8b17335ddb10a","tid":138920,"uid":2945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無嫁喇 硬食<br />\n鬼叫你係新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條友而家坐咗喺到撳電話"},{"pid":"4b0ae9317797a93c7047045d5aa8960a96050df6","tid":138920,"uid":2945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捐落佢枱底</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24574f80b91e3763ef3ac1b68d87ae005b3b3a2","tid":138920,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"比位你上炸朦撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4492cef0c1d90ed1f90ccc7227c9da003e9da1","tid":138920,"uid":2945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比位你上炸朦撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個post冇得升<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}